## Customization

Blue Dragon is designed to be customizable to suit your project's unique requirements. You can modify the provided UI elements and functionalities to match your desired look and behavior.

Refer to the [Customization Guide](docs/customization.md) for detailed instructions on customizing Blue Dragon. It covers topics such as CSS classes, configuration options, and advanced customization techniques.

